<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Kerri-Anne Kennerley was one of 25 employees to be sacked from Channel Ten as a cost-cutting measure last month. </p>

<p>Speaking to The Daily Telegraph's Confidential on Monday, the 66-year-old veteran journalist revealed she's leaving Studio 10 this week without any fanfare.</p>

<p>'I'm not having a going away party or anything like that,' she said.  </p>

<p>'There's no party': Axed Channel Ten star Kerri-Anne Kennerley (pictured), 66, is leaving Studio 10 this week without any fanfare</p>

<p>Last month, Channel Ten made 25 employees redundant, including Kerri-Anne, newsreader Natarsha Belling and weatherman Tim Bailey.   </p>

<p>On a recent episode of Studio 10, Kerri-Anne fought back tears as she acknowledged that the coronavirus pandemic had made it necessary to tighten the budget.   </p>

<p>She also thanked her friends and colleagues for their support. </p>

<p>Quiet send-off: 'I'm not having a going away party or anything like that,' the veteran journalist told The Daily Telegraph's Confidential on Monday</p>

<p>Axed: Last month, Channel Ten made 25 employees redundant, including Kerri-Anne (left), newsreader Natarsha Belling (right) and weatherman Tim Bailey </p>

<p>'I just know I'm back on the "lazy Susan" of television. Yeah, it's very, very tough for a lot of people,' she said on-air. </p>

<p>On Saturday, it was announced Tristan MacManus will join Sarah Harris as co-host on Studio 10.</p>

<p>The Dancing With The Stars judge, 38, will appear on the revamped program as of September 14. </p>

<p>New gig: On Saturday, it was announced Dancing With The Stars judge Tristan MacManus (pictured), 38, will join Sarah Harris as co-host on the revamped Studio 10 </p>

<p>New look: Tristan will appear on the revamped program alongside Sarah (pictured) as of September 14 </p>

<p>Tristan and Sarah will be joined by news reporter Narelda Jacobs, entertainment reporter Angela Bishop, and contributors Denise Drysdale, Jono Coleman and Craig Bennett. </p>

<p>Joe Hildebrand recently revealed on The Kyle and Jackie O Show that he has been offered 'a new role' and is in talks with the network about 'what that might be'. </p>

<p>Tristan said of his new role in an official statement: 'Although people know me as a dancer, I think my mouth usually works better than my feet do.</p>

<p>'This opportunity came out of the blue and I'm really excited to be working with Sarah and learning from her,' the father-of-two continued.  </p>

<p>New chapter: Studio 10's Joe Hildebrand (pictured) revealed on The Kyle and Jackie O Show that he has been offered 'a new role' and is in talks with the network about 'what that might be' </p>
